            <thetext>Support the notion of a &#39;default job&#39; that will be run if the generator is invoked without a job argument (like simply &#39;make&#39; would run the first job in the makefile). Since this has to depend on the current config  file, it should be a feature of the config file, not the generator itself.</thetext>
